text: Fatikh Saubanovich Sibagatullin (; ; 1 May 1950 â€“ 24 June 2022) was a Russian politician. He was a member of United Russia. He was in the State Duma from 2007 to 2021. Sibagatullin was born in Tatar ASSR, Russian SFSR, Soviet Union. Sibagatullin died at a hospital in Moscow, Russia from cardiac arrest on 24 June 2022 at the age of 72. ==References== Category:1950 births Category:2022 deaths Category:Members of the State Duma Category:Politicians from Tatarstan
